    "question_id" : 2254435,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Since you ask for another way to accomplish your goal, I suggest you use a wrapper class:</p>\n\n<pre><code>new Integer(null);\n</code></pre>\n"
