    "question_id" : 2254435,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<h2>No, but <strong>int[]</strong> can be.</h2>\n\n<pre><code>int[] hayhay = null; //: allowed (int[] is reference type)\nint   hayno  = null; //: error   (int   is primitive type)\n                     //: Message: incompatible types: \n                     //: &lt;null&gt; cannot be converted to int\n</code></pre>\n"
