    "question_id" : 2254435,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>instead of declaring as <code>int i</code> declare it as <code>Integer i</code> then we can do <code>i=null;</code></p>\n\n<pre><code>Integer i;\ni=null;\n</code></pre>\n"
