    "answer_id" : 57176571,
    "question_id" : 2254435,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Any Primitive data type like int,boolean, or float etc can't store the null(lateral),since java has provided Wrapper class for storing the same like int to Integer,boolean to Boolean.</p>\n\n<p>Eg: Integer i=null;</p>\n"
